<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> comport oneself with something • comport with something</xh5><p> <i>comport oneself with something—</i>behave in the way mentioned: With the help of a few drinks, the Consul <u>comports himself with</u> astounding aplomb.</p><p> <i>comport with something—</i>go well with smth.; be in harmony with smth.: Working for people in need <u>comports with</u> his beliefs and desire to help people.</p> </entry>
